Unseen_LLAMA_ZS_OpenStack_4:
10.11.10.1 "GET /v2/<*>/servers/detail HTTP/1.1" status: <*> len: <*> time: <*>


### Solution:

```python
def get_template(log):
    log = log.split(' ')
    template = ''
    for i in range(len(log)):
        if i % 2 == 0:
            template += log[i] +''
        else:
            template += '<*> '
    return template
```
